{"tid":2444805,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾國衛：普選不能夠只是強調循序漸進","createTime":"2021-03-13T06:25:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T06:38:30.000Z","uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f9571913bb54bc9f4c13aa86951dd8c8ab5fd93d","tid":2444805,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T06:25:05.000Z","msg":"政制及內地事務局長曾國衛認為, 全國人大會議通過完善香港選舉制度的決定, 並非不符循序漸進原則.<br />\n        曾國衛在電台節目指, 基本法規定, 根據香港的實際情況, 和循序漸進原則達至普選, 但坊間這段時間, 很多只是強調循序漸進, 而忽略了實際情況, 認為兩者都要考慮.<br />\n        他指, 目前的選舉制度下, 無法識別愛國者或非愛國者, 以致一些反中亂港人士有機會進入議會, 要針對實際情況作改善, 才有機會重回正軌, 又指, 完善香港選舉制度令事情更好, 有更優質的民主, 亦是一種進步.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/News/live.aspx?SearchText=&amp;NewsId=20210313100739&amp;page=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2FNews%2Flive.aspx%3FSearchText%3D%26NewsId%3D20210313100739%26page%3D0&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI76sSahl6lMEnfwETMIwf14%3D&h=e9702e5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/News/live.aspx?SearchText=&amp;NewsId=20210313100739&amp;page=0</a>"},{"pid":"a3db694b63fab72e06557f5e2efada0490e358f4","tid":2444805,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T06:25:49.000Z","msg":"//要針對實際情況作改善//<br />\n<br />\n龍門任我搬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b0fd81dd3fd7c38ad3c67bd1e67bcd5a669b1e","tid":2444805,"uid":64702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T06:26:39.000Z","msg":"滅市政局個下已經係倒退 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a2baaa08b5d67dbf4636ebbc07bd9c3f818120","tid":2444805,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41b0fd81dd3fd7c38ad3c67bd1e67bcd5a669b1e","tid":2444805,"uid":64702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T06:26:39.000Z","msg":"滅市政局個下已經係倒退 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T